  Name: TurnOne
  Dialogue:
  - Charecter: 1
    Text: '"Cardinal, fisherman are telling tales of gaping maws from Hell consuming
      the very oceans!"'
  - Charecter: 2
    Text: '"Such tales are folly. You cannot beleve the words of peasants, they are
      not men of the cloth."'
  - Charecter: 1
    Text: '"Yes, your Eminence. I shall have these heretics put to the sword immediately."  '
